-- EU Commission Will Present Pathway to 2050 CO2-Reduction Target Next Year
-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a
-- 2010-09-30T14:05:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/eu-commission-will-present-pathway-to-2050-co2-reduction-target-next-year.html
The European Union regulator plans
to propose in the first quarter of next year a scenario on
reaching its 2050 carbon emissions-reduction target.  The proposal will include a guiding interim target for
2030, Michael Starbaek Christensen, deputy chief of cabinet for
the EU climate commissioner, said today in Brussels.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ewa Krukowska in Brussels at 
 ekrukowska@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
